description.narrative: The Nepal Country programme 2018-2022 is built on the national priorities and in line with the UNICEF Strategic Plan. Implementing successfully this programme requires effective and efficient operational support translated into operational effectiveness outcome. The Operational effectiveness in turn is translated into 2 operational priorities in the AMP as follow: (1) Improved operational support for effective and efficient delivery of programme in the context of the federalism and (2) Improved office results through support to the governance and implementation of the re-positioning of the operations functions. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:10/01/2020
